        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Educators Expense Deduction Modernization Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill increases the tax deduction for the expenses of eligible educators from $250 to $1,000, An<em> eligible educator </em>is, with respect to any taxable year, an individual who is a kindergarten through grade 12 teacher, instructor, counselor, principal, or aide in a school for at least 900 hours during a school year.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
